data.description: Welcome Home!!! This cozy and inviting new construction home is a must see. The open floor concept offers split bedrooms, plenty of windows for natural light, decorative lighting, crown molding and wood like ceramic tile through out.  The kitchen features wood shaker cabinets with granite countertops, a large kitchen island and stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom, which is off the living room offers a beautiful bathroom with a large walk in closet, dual sinks and a large shower with double heads and two seat benches.  The backyard has a covered patio, wood deck and a storage shed out back.  This home is located close to shopping and all major highways.
